				<pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2013 23:04:36 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Derp Tape</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1694191</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Seriously, the disappearing from one side of town and appearing on the other made me visualize this town as a weird warped 3d Pac-Man level.</p> <p>this SCP really is well worded and easily followed, which is no mean feat when working on temporal dynamics. A great twist on the whole stuck in a time loop genre, well done.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
